text: @FedExHelp I don’t understand the delivery manager app. It says on my door tag that “you decide when your packages are delivered”. I need need mine to be delivered after 5:30 PM EST - how in the world am I supposed to specify this when there is no option to do so on the app?

@unrulygrl Hi, this is Kelly. I do apologize for any for any frustration or inconvenience. I will be happy to check on your delivery options. Please DM @FedExHelp with your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number and email address.
